        </tr>
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">6.2.</td>
            <td>If the Vocalizr PayPal account - <a href="mailto:payments@vocalizr.com">payments@vocalizr.com</a> (Payment Service) is used and there is no offer and acceptance of any royalty, then the
