    <table class="decimal-list" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
        <tr valign="top">
            <td class="num">10.1.</td>
            <td>Payments are only to be made through the Vocalizr Payment Service. The Employee and
                Employer agree not to circumvent Vocalizr's Payment Service by (but not limited to): soliciting work with
